From {{log4j.properties}}:

The default logging for anything is Confluence is WARN:

{code}log4j.rootLogger=WARN, confluencelog, errorlog{code}

However, the default logging level for plugins is INFO:

{code}# Plugins can use "atlassian.plugin" loggers across all products (Platform 2.7 requirement)
log4j.logger.atlassian.plugin=INFO
{code}

Team Calendar's package is: {{com.atlassian.confluence.extra.calendar3}}, so it doesn't receive the extra plugin logging.

